> **Farzana says:** "Natural cushion pendants make sense for one buyer: someone giving this as a gift that is meant to last. A lab pendant is beautiful jewelry. A natural cushion pendant is a piece with the story of a real stone from the ground. If that story matters to the person receiving it, the $4,312 difference at 1ct has a reason. For everyone else, buy lab."

