## Expert Summary

Cushion cut diamond necklace pendants run from [$700 (1/4 ct lab)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-solitaire-pendant-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251295?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) to [$2,674 (3 ct lab)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-solitaire-pendant-in-14k-white-gold-3-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251305?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational), and natural from [$1,190 (1/4 ct)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/cushion-cut-diamond-solitaire-pendant-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251293?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) to [$5,460 (1 ct)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/cushion-cut-diamond-solitaire-pendant-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251300?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). All solitaire styles are currently 30% off certified market pricing.

The [lab 1 ct at $1,148](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-solitaire-pendant-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251302?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the right call for most buyers. It lands in The Pendant Sweet Spot — clearly visible at collarbone distance, appropriate for daily wear and occasions, and F-G/VS2-SI1 quality. The [2 ct at $1,785](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-solitaire-pendant-in-14k-white-gold-2-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251304?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the best value jump in the range if your budget allows.

Remember The Colour Cut Advantage. A cushion pendant catches ambient light differently than a round — the big facets show the stone's body colour and depth as it moves. That's why coloured diamond pendants almost always use cushion or radiant cuts. For a colourless white cushion pendant, it's a more contemplative, warmer sparkle than round. For a natural coloured cushion, the colour saturation is noticeably stronger.

Metal choice: white gold for clean and crisp, yellow gold for warmth and character, platinum for maximum durability with a small premium.

